query: SELECT se.id, se.studentId, se.subjectId, se.professorId, se.status, st.fullName as student_name, sub.name as subject_name FROM student_enrollments se LEFT JOIN students st ON se.studentId = st.id LEFT JOIN subjects sub ON se.subjectId = sub.id LIMIT 10;
